Author: dragaynite
Text: I lose my appetite everytime someone is in the kitchen when I’m grabbing food. It makes me so ANGRY that someone sees me getting food. They don’t even have to say anything to me, they just have to exist in the same room as me

Author: hondaceviche
Text: Anytime I'm getting a snack and my mom goes "whatcha doin?" I wanna lose it. She's just asking like, what I'm up to today.  Also my boyfriend goes "how's your [food] baby?" and it drives me insane for no good reason. :/
